via `kotlin.KotlinVersion.CURRENT`\n  - `callStaticMethod(...)` via `scala.util.Properties.versionNumberString()`\n- Asserted that the runtime metadata header includes detected `kt` and `sc` major/minor entries.\n- Made the existing top-level `Elasticsearch_javaTest` class `public` to satisfy test-class visibility rules.\n\nFiles changed:\n- `tests/src/co.elastic.clients/elasticsearch-java/9.0.3/build.gradle`\n- `tests/src/co.elastic.clients/elasticsearch-java/9.0.3/src/test/java/co_elastic_clients/elasticsearch_java/Elasticsearch_javaTest.java`\n- `tests/src/co.elastic.clients/elasticsearch-java/9.0.3/src/test/java/co_elastic_clients/elasticsearch_java/LanguageRuntimeVersionsTest.java`\n\nTests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_096af9234d5bb14c016a40e82d28908197881d29a865bdd65b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2824, "output": 1697, "cacheRead": 45056, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49577, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782638616088, "responseId": "resp_096af9234d5bb14c016a40e81939d48197a7caed89b22849bc"}, "toolResults": []}
